Package: atradio
Version: 0.5.1
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Tsiry Sandratraina <tsiry.sndr@rocksky.app>
Homepage: https://github.com/tsirysndr/atradio.fm
Depends: libc6, libasound2
Description: A TUI radio player on the AT Protocol
 atradio brings atradio.fm to your terminal: browse trending / popular
 stations, fuzzy-search the whole radio-browser directory, play live
 streams with a full Rockbox DSP/equalizer chain, and — when signed in —
 favorite stations and post comments to your own PDS. On Linux the player
 is exposed over MPRIS for media-key and desktop integration.
